Package net.mcreator.ui.modgui

Interface ModElementChangedListener

All Superinterfaces:
ActionListener, ChangeListener, DocumentListener, EventListener, ItemListener, KeyListener, MouseListener
public interface ModElementChangedListener extends MouseListener, KeyListener, ActionListener, ItemListener, ChangeListener, DocumentListener

Gets triggered whenever a change to a mod element is detected inside ModElementGUI

One case of this listener usage is warning the user about some unsaved changes made to a mod element. Another case is the ModElementCodeViewer which regenerates the code preview upon UI changes.
